{"tid":835204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"力爭女權收死亡恐嚇 危地馬拉婦女組織領袖遭當街槍殺","createTime":"2018-09-24T16:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T17:16:35.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ac2e93d8c07b08b0fab8d83749009bf50be344f4","tid":835204,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180923/large/1537692452_0dbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180923%2Flarge%2F1537692452_0dbb.jpg&h=b7b4de67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被槍殺的聖地亞哥是當地婦女組織領袖(互聯網)<br />\n危地馬拉一個婦女組織的領袖，日前遭數名身分不明人士槍殺，她此前因致力支援受暴力對待的婦女，曾收過死亡恐嚇。<br />\n57歲死者聖地亞哥（Juana Ramirez Santiago）是「伊克西婦女網絡」（Network of Ixil Women）的領袖，亦是一名助產士。危地馬拉人權捍衞組織的聲明指，槍擊發生在內巴赫鎮（Nebaj）附近的村莊，事發當晚聖地亞哥正送飯給丈夫，據指2名年輕兇徒共向她開4槍，她當場死亡。<br />\n聯合國人權事務高級專員公署危地馬拉辦事處譴責事件，並對聖地亞哥的親友致以慰問，希望當地檢察官可以秉公辦理。人權捍衞組織的紀錄亦顯示，今年1月至6月已發生135宗針對維權人士的襲擊、13宗謀殺2宗企圖謀殺案。<br />\n中央社／拉丁美洲南方電視台  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180924/58714442\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180924%2F58714442&d=M%2FWFs1TfR0HRUN0%2BgqfCnV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=13424abd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180924%2F58714442&h=cb83b75a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180924/58714442</a>"},{"pid":"97b2f03e4e67ff78f78cd6fce7996c2858fb19dc","tid":835204,"uid":35699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"咁果個唔係恐嚇，係死亡通知啦"},{"pid":"c581e367e6b7ef23fa890559f2c45e97ec22e295","tid":835204,"uid":53687,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"呢啲真女權值得尊重"},{"pid":"b31f6aea9220206283bae3b9fb0e55096ae34cd7","tid":835204,"uid":49197,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"抵,殺得好"},{"pid":"043cb919a387acc47898ea12d53e82e087d65245","tid":835204,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c581e367e6b7ef23fa890559f2c45e97ec22e295","tid":835204,"uid":53687,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"呢啲真女權值得尊重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T17:09:09.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"dc0750d01ffec2f63c7572ddc097f813a78c39bc","tid":835204,"uid":24265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b31f6aea9220206283bae3b9fb0e55096ae34cd7","tid":835204,"uid":49197,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"抵,殺得好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"點解唔係殺你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81d958cb5cbca69520cff30ffd90e8a14e329da","tid":835204,"uid":192158,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T17:12:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46363e3db454bf70c0876d2abcfb560eb1329562","tid":835204,"uid":81183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T17:16:35.000Z","msg":"睇到危地馬拉4隻字之前都想講抵撚死<br />\n但係危地馬拉呢d地方既女權真係值得尊重，rip<br />\n希望西方d女權西去呢d地方爭取女權，唔好on99 係有晒法律保障你既地方去爭取"}]}